This is my Smart Door. 

Step 1: Run create_database.py - This will create the database

Step 2: Run record_faces.py - This will create a data set of the users face using the Pi Camera

Step 3: Run trainer.py - This will train the data set for facial recognition

Step 4: Run pull.py & - This first script will run in the background and handle the door lock from the Android Device

Step 5: Run face_recognition.py - This is the main facial recognition script